$ vim Hello.java

Normal Mode			[Esc]
Insert Mode			i
Normal Mode operations
	Force close 		:q![Enter]
	Save and close		:wq![Enter]	OR	:x![Enter]
	Basic Navigation	:set number[Enter]	// To set the line numbers
				:line number[Enter]	//To go to specific line
	Save			:w![Enter]
	Basic Editing		
				:dd	//Deleting the line having cursor
				:u	// Undo command
				:v	//Highlighting, selecting and deselecting by arrow keys (Visual Mode)
				:y	// yank mode (Copy the selected text to clipboard)
				:o	// creating a new line
				:p	// Paste the content
	Basic Searching	/keyword to search
	Concurrent Files	:split filename or :vsplit filename 	// Horizontal or vertical split
				Press [ctrl]ww to switch the screen
	
